  "description": "Explore vast worlds, fight formidable enemies, and build your kingdom. A RPG fantasy styled modpack for 1.20.1",
  "body": "<center><p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/x3EtxHlO/images/e2cfdb738e2c451f34af638a8d0e64bfd367faf0.png\" width=\"699\" height=\"138\" alt=\"Lazr's Pack header\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Meant for the supporters of Lazr's Mods, this modpack contains all of the mods Lazr has made along with a few mods for a fantasy style survival experience.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This modpack contains over 200 mods aiming to provide the player with a simple fantasy rpg survival experience. Explore revamped vanilla biomes along side beautiful modded biomes. Find many structures of ancient civilizations and use their knowledge to construct great kingdoms.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Requires <strong>~5</strong> GB of RAM</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr /><center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Support me on Liberapay<br/><a href=\"https://liberapay.com/LazrProductions/donate\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://liberapay.com/assets/widgets/donate.svg\" alt=\"Donate using Liberapay\"></a></p><center/><hr/>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> Feel free to join our discord! </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/pwn35yhwrG\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1139438885944954970/1139632750786252891/discordbutton.png\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\" alt=\"discord icon\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p><br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/lazr\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/fa820d42-3c60-4f73-ae5d-476